725016f-b.text:
12th Street, west side, at 26th Avenue, viewing north and showing a row of fashionable private homes. 26th Avenue was cut through here where the second house from the left is seen. These buildings appear on maps after 1891. 12th Street was
formely Remsen Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 14, 1931
